[quote]
[h2]⚠️Using [b]HEROES OF SYX[/b] / New Games Start with Negative Gov Points? [/h2]
This only applies to new games; existing saves can ignore this. To run Heroes of Syx alongside Create-A-Culture, you [i]must[/i] enable CaC only [i]after[/i] you've generated your world and placed your throne.

[b]Instructions[/b]
Specifically, 1. start a new game with HoS [i][b]enabled[/b][/i] and CaC [i][b]disabled[/b][/i], 2. let the world generate, and place your throne. 3. Then save the game and relaunch with [b][i]both mods enabled[/i][/b] and you're good-to-go. You now don't need to do this ever again for that save game.

You'll need to repeat these steps whenever you create a new game (i.e. whenever world generation would take place).
[/quote]